metadata.description:
Sequences, repetitions, transpositions and retrogrades of line and arc movements within a small grid.

@erikswahn 

2021

This is a canvas with a balance of colors and shapes. It depicts an abstract landscape of another planet. The letter that appears in some iterations comes from this NFT hash. At the right top corner you can get features.

Features:

Palette: one of 10 palettes;
Shape1: 'spaceship', 'planet' or 'none' – the rectangle or circle above;
Shape2: 'iceberg', 'mountain, 'none';
SpacePattern: 'laser', 'stars', 'none' – cosmos pattern;
Waves: the waves at the water;
Transport: from 0 to 2 – I'm bet someone use them as a transport;
Letter: One of the letter from yours NFT hash
Clouds: has clouds or not, was used font and symbol ☁
Background Pattern: 'circle', '+', 'lines' or 'none'
Monochrome: is pallet is monochrome, makes all monochrome
Framed: has the tiny frame or not.
